description:
Jack Posobiec is joined by Darren Beattie of Revolver News to provide updates on all things censorship, from the DHS to Twitter. Beattie exposes DiResta’s Dark Alabama Secret and how she ginned up her career utilizing fake Russian accounts. Meanwhile, Biden’s mission creep is revealed after news surfaces that active-duty U.S. military members are conducting ‘inspections’ in Ukraine. 



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
